      '<strong>Key Risk:</strong> Regulatory escalation (CN¥1B+ fine or forced business change) is the primary bear driver — 5-8pp EBITDA impact. Douyin capex blitz in lower-tier cities risks 3-5pp share erosion. Kling capex overrun if revenue misses US$150M — modest margin drag but not existential.',
