    betterAlt: '<span class="alt-ticker">N/A</span> Tencent 20x+ P/E with lower growth. Bilibili negative ROIC + structural headwind. ByteDance (Douyin) private. Kuaishou is the only investable proxy for China short-video duopoly at best combination of SQ, growth, and valuation discount.',
